\chapter{Guidance for the Preparation of Material Submittals}

Please follow these instructions carefully in order to process the material submittal speedily.

1. All submittals, however minor must be accompanied by a Compliance Statement.

1.  All columns must be completed. If you comply with a clause please just state "Comply". If your product does not comply just state "DO NOT COMPLY" and in the remarks column add any notes you wish to support your product. Do not use words such as noted or excluded.


2. All material submittals to be provided in 6 copies (2 Engineer, 1 HLG, 1 Records, 1 Head-Office Record) 1 Engineering Office.

3. Two of the submittals must provide original catalogues.

4. Highlight in yellow the exact selection, if the catalogue is of a more general nature.





